data.description: Welcome to this secluded beautifully update split-level in Marlington schools! Pulling up the long gravel drive you are welcomed to the home and a large 30 x 50 pole barn built in 2005. Walking into the front door you enter into the completely remodeled home, the living room has beautiful natural wood floors with adorable shiplap wall for coats or backpacks for the kids! Walking into the kitchen, its beautifully updated with granite countertops and new handles. Dishwasher, stove and microwave stay. Moving down into the large family room has a wood burning fireplace with the mantal added in 2022. A fully updated 1/2 bath perfect for when guests are over! Going down into the basement area is a perfect mancave with a bar, stools and shelving that stay! Making way up to the third level is all three bedrooms, great closet spaces! Master bedroom has a fully updated master bath with a corner shower! Full bathroom on third level fully updated also! Updates include recently: Mancave added 2022, ductwork cleaned 2022, sump pump 2022, shiplap 2022, kitchen hardware 2022, garbage disposal 2022, sliding backdoor 2021, graveled driveway and barn 2022. Schedule a showing today!
